---
---

<section
  class="nothyp-section"
  style="background: #101e35; padding: 5rem 2.5rem;"
>
  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem;">
      <h2
        style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem); color: #F5F0E8; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.2;"
      >
        This is not hypothetical.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div
      class="nothyp-grid"
      style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem;"
    >
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div
        style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;"
      >
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 2.8rem; color: #C49A2B; margin: 0; line-height: 1;"
        >
          $47,000
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8B9CAF; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; flex: 1;"
        >
          An 11-day agent loop. Two AIs talking to each other. Nobody noticed.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://techstartups.com/2025/11/14/ai-agents-horror-stories-how-a-47000-failure-exposed-the-hype-and-hidden-risks-of-multi-agent-systems/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(196,154,43,0.45); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;"
          onmouseover="this.style.color='#C49A2B'"
          onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(196,154,43,0.45)'"
        >Source &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div
        style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;"
      >
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 2.8rem; color: #C49A2B; margin: 0; line-height: 1;"
        >
          $2,400
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8B9CAF; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; flex: 1;"
        >
          One night. One malformed PDF. The agent never stopped trying.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://altersquare.io/ai-coding-tools-2026-used-across-20-client-projects/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(196,154,43,0.45); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;"
          onmouseover="this.style.color='#C49A2B'"
          onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(196,154,43,0.45)'"
        >Source &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div
        style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;"
      >
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 2.8rem; color: #C49A2B; margin: 0; line-height: 1;"
        >
          $22,000/mo
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8B9CAF; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; flex: 1;"
        >
          Token overages. 200 developers rolled back. 30 caused 70% of the damage.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://altersquare.io/ai-coding-tools-2026-used-across-20-client-projects/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; color: rgba(196,154,43,0.45); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;"
          onmouseover="this.style.color='#C49A2B'"
          onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(196,154,43,0.45)'"
        >Source &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nothyp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
